{"tid":669222,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【悲劇英雄】Zemo 同 Killmonger 都係比黑豹呢個反派收皮","createTime":"2018-05-18T09:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T11:23:19.000Z","uid":61443,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7ef1f27dda264874e8845a5e41d74dda106b0a88","tid":669222,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T09:39:35.000Z","msg":"Zemo (真英雄) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n背景：復仇者2 受害者 <br />\n目的：瓦解復仇者<br />\n理念：內部破壞先係最強 <br />\n<br />\n人地zemo都諗住最後自殺找數 <br />\n仆佢個街黑豹阻撚住晒<br />\nzemo應該比人鎖撚住成世 <br />\n<br />\nKillmonger (真英雄) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n背景：黑人受害者<br />\n目的：利用瓦干達科技拯救同族<br />\n理念：黑人唔應該受壓迫<br />\n<br />\n人地跟程序有能力贏個皇位返嚟 <br />\n黑豹小學雞唔認輸 <br />\n打到最後黑豹係有經驗醒左 <br />\n知道上次害鳩左zemo <br />\nKillmonger 就死果陣保險問多次你想唔想死 <br />\nKillmonger 真男人唔駛壞人出手救 <br />\n同埋知道救返又好似zemo咁坐一世 <br />\n<br />\nZemo 同 Killmonger 呢2個悲劇英雄<br />\n如果佢地一早認識對方<br />\n世界可能會經變得美好過冇左一半人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52336ffdc2428548df076743bcd3e4f89b00beb2","tid":669222,"uid":174654,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T09:46:08.000Z","msg":"我就睇下樓豬可以開到幾多個mcu post"},{"pid":"d41fac1bc63fd30a72e8901b075c29a19c4a6925","tid":669222,"uid":19867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T09:47:15.000Z","msg":"Killmonger似係想黑人統治全世界wo<br />\n你肯定呢個行為係叫做英雄?"},{"pid":"fde4446246e479878a7b546282e2bbe25eeb07d6","tid":669222,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"52336ffdc2428548df076743bcd3e4f89b00beb2","tid":669222,"uid":174654,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T09:46:08.000Z","msg":"我就睇下樓豬可以開到幾多個mcu post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T09:47:18.000Z","msg":"利伸: 隊長fans <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7